# Design System: Next-Gen Fintech (2025–2026)

## 1. Color System

### Brand Foundation
Derived from the official Market Pulse AI logo — do not deviate from these values.

| Role                | Hex       | Description                                        |
|---------------------|-----------|----------------------------------------------------|
| Primary (Anchor)    | `#0A2540` | Deep navy — sidebar, nav, headings, icon base      |
| Action (Cyan)       | `#00B4FF` | Electric cyan — "AI" wordmark, buttons, highlights |
| Gradient Start      | `#1A6BCC` | Logo icon gradient midpoint (navy → cyan)          |
| Gradient End        | `#00D4FF` | Logo icon gradient tip (brightest cyan)            |
| Background (Light)  | `#F6F9FC` | Low-strain canvas for data-heavy views             |
| Background (Dark)   | `#121212` | Soft black — never use pure `#000000`              |

### Brand Gradient (Logo-Derived)
Use this gradient for the logo icon, hero accents, chart fills, and primary CTAs:
```css
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2540 0%, #1A6BCC 50%, #00D4FF 100%);
```
For text gradients (e.g., "AI" wordmark replication):
```css
background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1A6BCC, #00D4FF);
-webkit-background-clip: text;
-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
```

### Semantic Status Palette
Always pair status colors with icons or text labels — never rely on color alone.

| Status          | Light Mode  | Dark Mode   | Usage                        |
|-----------------|-------------|-------------|------------------------------|
| Success/Profit  | `#198754`   | `#4CAF50`   | Bullish signals, gains       |
| Danger/Loss     | `#DC3545`   | `#F44336`   | Bearish, crash risk, losses  |
| Warning/Pending | `#FFC107`   | `#FFB300`   | Medium risk, neutral signals |
| Info/Neutral    | `#0DCAF0`   | `#03A9F4`   | Informational, metadata      |

### Dark Mode Elevation (No Shadows)
Use lighter background tones to indicate depth — NOT box shadows:
- Base canvas: `#121212`
- Card surface: `#1E1E1E`
- Elevated modal/overlay: `#2A2A2A`
- Tooltip / glass overlay: translucent `#1E1E1E` + `backdrop-filter: blur(12px)`

Reduce saturation of vibrant colors by 10–20% in dark mode to prevent visual "vibration."

