## 4. Design Token Architecture

### Naming Convention: Category–Property–Modifier
```css
/* Colors */
--color-button-primary-bg: #635BFF;
--color-surface-card: #1E1E1E;       /* dark */
--color-surface-base: #121212;       /* dark */
--color-feedback-error-text: #F44336;
--color-feedback-success-text: #4CAF50;
--color-feedback-warning-text: #FFB300;

/* Spacing */
--spacing-layout-margin: 1.5rem;
--spacing-card-padding: 1.25rem;

/* Typography */
--font-primary: 'Inter', sans-serif;
--font-mono: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
--font-brand: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
```

### Tailwind Config Mapping
Map all tokens to Tailwind custom colors so they're usable as utility classes:
```ts
// tailwind.config.ts
colors: {
  anchor: '#0A2540',         // Primary navy (logo wordmark, sidebar)
  brand: {
    cyan: '#00B4FF',         // Action / "AI" accent
    mid: '#1A6BCC',          // Gradient midpoint
    bright: '#00D4FF',       // Gradient tip
  },
  surface: { base: '#121212', card: '#1E1E1E', elevated: '#2A2A2A' },
  profit: { DEFAULT: '#4CAF50', light: '#198754' },
  loss: { DEFAULT: '#F44336', light: '#DC3545' },
  warning: { DEFAULT: '#FFB300', light: '#FFC107' },
  info: { DEFAULT: '#03A9F4', light: '#0DCAF0' },
}
```

